unittitle_ssm: Faculty of Arts and Science Department of Music Student Composition Recordings and Concert Ephemera
abstract_ssm: The Faculty of Arts and Science Department of Music Student Composition Recordings and Concert Ephemera consists of 147 audiovisual recordings of new music compositions by students of the FAS Music Department. Audio recordings of performances, rehearsals, and studio sessions constitute the vast majority of the collection's materials, though it also contains four video recordings of interviews with visiting composer Elliott Carter. One folder of print and manuscript ephemera accompanies the audio recordings.
